title: Atherosclerotic Cardiovascular Disease
description: This value set may undergo changes until the HL7 Multiple Chronic Care FHIR IG is formally published in 2024.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values addresses terms representing Atherosclerotic Cardiovascular Disease.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this set of values is to identify patients who have a/an documented diagnosis of atherosclerotic cardiovascular disease.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes GROUP codes for Atherosclerotic Cardiovascular Disease.),(Exclusion Criteria: Terms not representative of observable encoded terms that may have values indicating Atherosclerotic Cardiovascular Disease.)
